Title: Seiko "NEO-SPORT" Chronograph. Unusual, imported model. 7T92-0NG0. circa Dec '12
Description: Seiko Chronograph 7t92-0NG0 This is a superb example of a Seiko Neo-Sport ion plated model.Very unusual, only produced for around 12 months before being discontinued.Classic heavy-duty 7t92 calibre chronograph. ** Case **Highly polished black steel (ion plated).44.5mm case diameter, 47.5mm with crown.Edge-to-edge mineral glass (flat). ** Bracelet**Original Seiko M0R9-D-W bracelet. Also ion plated steel.18mm hidden/hooded lug fitting.Fold over locking clasp.Length is approx 7.50" fastened. Four removable links in the bracelet. ** Dial **Matt black dial with sub-dials ringed in white.White minute/hour hands with lume centres. White chronograph handsHour markers are plain white and etched under the glass.Date at 4 position. ** Movement **Quartz 7t92 calibre chronograph.Times in 1/20th second increments up to 12 hours. ** Condition **Exceptional condition with almost no signs of wear. It keeps excellent time and all functions work correctly.Overall condition of the case and bracelet are near perfect.Mineral glass is good but has a very fine scratch.NO wear to the plating. ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~A very good example of a very scarce model, these are already thin on the ground and getting impossible to find in this condition.~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ Please be aware that I cannot guarantee water resistance on pre-owned watches.
